{"tid":2515234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺有個咩都要理既上司真係好撚煩？","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T23:45:15.000Z","uid":11097,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"811af24d6aa326989c3b4c161fdeb895fba96c3f","tid":2515234,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:33:44.000Z","msg":"上司就應該要做返上司既野<br />\n下下都踩線做埋你果份，都唔緊要<br />\n同你做埋當然最撚好<br />\n但每日都問你xxx做咗未，yyy做完未，zzz呢就嚟開波啦喎⋯⋯<br />\n緊張時期一返到公司早餐都未撚食就捉住你係咁講工事<br />\n見到你開波前抖下氣，坐係自己位又問你做乜撚野唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始覺得佢似啲煩閪多過似你上司<br />\n仲要唔識做人，因為佢自己偏執既性格攪撚到你變左同其他Dpt既磨心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個好既上司應該知咩時候放手俾下屬做自己野<br />\n定<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個好既上司應該好似老母湊仔咁睇住自己下屬做野"},{"pid":"fb28b6e0faf27940d8705fca276852d7a3d3eccc","tid":2515234,"uid":209750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:36:07.000Z","msg":"Micromanagement <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12cbbbb3e0fe3860438eac2cb70d8f413419108","tid":2515234,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb28b6e0faf27940d8705fca276852d7a3d3eccc","tid":2515234,"uid":209750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:36:07.000Z","msg":"Micromanagement <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:37:20.000Z","msg":"每日返工一諗起呢啲就心口悶<br />\n係咪已經開始有少少心理壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231b7478770762bd48f326be9f4d18ae583cca85","tid":2515234,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/